tafsir[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif, laam, raa: yewtere fii sugu …óee Aayeeje yawtiino ka arannde cortewol(simoore) Baqarah. ∆äee Aayeeje ko mawnu…óe fiyaaku, tinndin…óe wonnde ko …óe jippiniaa…óe ka Alla, Aayeeje Alqur'aana …ìanngin…óe tawhiidi e sari'aaji."
  15,2,"Heefer…ìe …ìen yeloyto √ëalnde Darngal, tuma fee√±anta …ìe meere keeferaaku ngu …ìe wonunoo e mun aduna, sinno …ìe laatino juul…ìe."
  15,3,"An Nulaa…óo, accu …ìee fennoo…ìe √±aamira no neemoraa…ói √±aamirta, …ìe dakmitora dakamme aduna lannay…óe, …ìe sokolira juutingol caate gaa gom…óinal e golle mo∆¥∆¥e. Aray …ìe annda ko …ìe wonunoo e hayrere kon, tuma …ìe darnoyaa yeeso Alla √ëalnde Darngal."
  15,4,"Men jippinaali halkaare e saare jeyaande e too√±unde, si wanaa hara no woodani nde lajal dot-tangal anndaangal ka Alla, ngal …ìeydotaako ngal …óuytotaako."
  15,5,"Mofte woo halketaake ado lajal majje timmude, …óe nennantaake …óum kadi si hewtii. Haani hara too√±oo…ìe …ìen …óaynitoraali ko Alla nennitirani …ìe kon."
  15,6,"Heefer…ìe makka …ìen wi'ani Nulaa…óo Alla on (yo o his): Ko an yo nodditii…óo jippineede e mun (Deftere nden), pellet aan e noddugol maa ko a kaangaa…óo ha…óa firlito pirlitagol feetu…óo."
  15,7,"Ko ha…ó Ma addande amen Malaykaaji …ói ceedo wonde ko a goon…óu…óo e nelal ma he e tellagol lepte."
  15,8,"Alla jaaborii ∆¥amol ma…ì…ìe addugol Malaa'ika ngol: Men jippinirtaa Malaa'ika si wanaa ko yahdata e √±een√±al, tuma hewti halkirgol …ìe lepte. ∆Åe wonoy- tah, tuma Men addoyta Malaa'ika, hara …ìe gom…ói- naali, leelnoytee…ìe, ko woni, …ìe yacciniroyte lepte …óen."
  15,9,"Ko Menen woni ko jippini ndee Alqur'aanaare e fonndo Muhammadu (jom-kisiyee) siftinore yim…ìe …ìen. Menen kadi ko Men reenoo…ìe nde e …ìeydee- de maa …óuyteede, maa walylee, wa…ótitee."
  15,10,"Gom…óii Men nuliino ado maa an Nulaa…óo, Nulaa…ìe goo, e le√±i yeddunoo…ìe ko adii, …ìe fenni …ìe. Wanaa an adaa fenneede e Nulaa…ìe …ìen."
  15,11,"Nulaa…óo woo araali e …óen mofte heefer…ìe adinoo…ìe, si wanaa …ìe fennay mo …ìe jalkita."
  15,12,"Ko wano Men naadirnoo fennugol ngol e …ìer…óe …óen mofte, Men naadirta …óum e …ìer…óe sirkoo…ìe Makka …ìen, sabu …óuurnagol …ìe townitoo ngol."
  15,13,"∆Åe gom…óintaa ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his), gom…óii sunna Alla on e halkugol fennu…ìe Nulaa…ìe mun …ìen yawtiino. Yo fennoo…ìe ma …ìen waajito."
  15,14,"∆Åee fennoo…ìe townitii…ìe, hay goonga kan fee√±irani …ìe hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói, hay Men udditanno …ìe damal ka kammu, …ìe wa…óti ∆¥awrude."
  15,15,"∆Åe goongintaano, …ìe wi'ayno : Anndee gite amen …óen hippa e yi'ugol. Wurin ko men yi'aynoo ko batte mbilewu, ko men mbilaa …ìe."
  15,16,"Gom…óii men wa…óii koode maw…óe ka kammu, …óe yim…ìe …ìen …óoworta e …óalle ma…ì…ìe, ka ni…ìe njorndi e ka maayo. Men wa…óaniri-…óe …ìen ndaaroo…ìe …óe fii yo …ìe dallinor…óe e kattal Alla ngal."
  15,17,"Men reeniri kammu ngun e kala seytaane riiwaa…óo e yurmeende Alla."
  15,18,"Si wanaa on he…óitanii…óo majannde dental ngal, hoodere jalbunde jokkita ngii, nde sumaa ngii."
  15,19,"Leydi ndin, Men weerti ndi ka yim…ìe …ìen daakoo, Men wa…ói e mayri pelle tabitu…óe fii wata ndi yergu e ma…ì…ìe. Men fu…óini e mayri noone kala e pu…ói, kon ko e…ì…ìaa happiraa hikma."
  15,20,"Men wa…óani on ka leydi ton, onon yim…ìe …ìen, ko wuuriron, immorde e √±aametee e njaram, fotde hi…óon e nguurndam aduna. Men wa…óani …ìen …ìe on arsikataa ka yim…ìe e ka kulle kadi ko …ìe wuurira."
  15,21,"Hunnde alaa nde yim…ìe e daabeeji …óin nafitorta, si wanaa Me…óen hattani woodingol nde ko …ìe nafitora. Men woodinaali kadi e nden huunde, si wanaa e e…ì…ìoore happaande yahdunde e √±en∆¥al e muy…óe Amen."
  15,22,"Men wurti keneeli …óin hawrondirooji e duule; Men jippiniri …óen duule to…ìo, Men yarniri on ndiyam to…ìo. Wonaa onon …ìee yim…ìe woni ko mari …óam ndiyam ka leydi, fii ko wona …ìulli e can…ói, ko Alla woni ko mari …óam ton."
  15,23,"Ko Menen kadi woni wuurnitiroo…ìe maay…ìe tagu- gol e waaseede, immintinoya …ìe …ìaawo maayde, Men wuurnita kadi maay…ìe si laje ma…ì…ìe timmii. Ko Menen woni heddotoo…ìe rona leydi ndin e ko woni e mayri."
  15,24,"Gom…óii Men anndii adii…ìe mon jibineede e maa-yoo…ìe, Men anndii kadi sakkitotoo…ìe e mun. Hunnde e …óum suu…óaaki Men."
  15,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, ko Kanko moo…ìoy- ta …ìe denndaangal √ëalnde Darngal, fii yo O yo…ìu mo∆¥∆¥in…óo on e bonnu…óo on. Kanko ko O √ëee√±u…óo e toppitagol Mo ngol, Anndu…óo Mo huunde suu…óaaki …óum."
  15,26,"Gom…óii Men tagirii Aadama e mbullaari yoorundi wa…óayndi hito si tappaama, ndin ko …ìaleeri waylorndi sabu nee…ìugol waalagol ndi."
  15,27,"Men tagiri baaba jinnaaji …óin ko adii tageede Aadama (yo o his) e yiite ooyunge."
  15,28,"Janto an Nulaa…óo, tuma nde Joomi maa dalannoo Malaa'ika'en e Ibuliisa wonndunoo…óo e ma…ì…ìe: Min Mi tagay …ìanndinke immorde e loopal yooru- yongal, wa…óayngal hito si tappaama, …ìalewal waylotoongal balangol."
  15,29,"Si Mi fotndindirii mo, Mi timminii tagugol mo, haray ko yo on suuyiran mo …óoftagol yamiroore Am e hiwraade mo."
  15,30,"Malaa'ika'en …óoftii yamiroore Joomi ma…ì…ìe, …ìe sujji …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe."
  15,31,"Ibuliisa kan -wonndunoo…óo e Malaa'ika'en kono mo jeyaaka e ma…ì…ìe- ha…óitii sujjanngol Aadama wonndude e Malaa'ika'en."
  15,32,"Alla daalani Ibuliisa …ìaawo o ha…óitaade sujjangol Aadama: E ko ha…óu maa sujjidugol e Malaa'ika'en …ìen sujjir…ìe …óoftagol yamiroore Am?"
  15,33,"Ibuliisa jaabori townitaare: Sellantaa lam ka mi sujjanta …ìanndinke mo Tagu…óaa immorde e loopal yoorungal, …ìalewal waylotongal."
  15,34,"Alla daalani ibuliisa: Yaltu ka Aljanna, sabu ko a riiwaa…óo."
  15,35,"Pellet, kuddi e riiweede e yurmeende Am fawike e ma haa √ëalnde Darngal."
  15,36,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Joomi am, nennitanam hara A waraa-ni lam haa √±ande tagu gun immintinoytee."
  15,37,"Alla daalani mo: An on, ko a jeyaa…óo e nennitanaa…ìe laje mun …ìen."
  15,38,"Haa e √±alaande nde fow maayata nden si allaadu ndun wuttaama araunuru."
  15,39,"Ibuliisa wi'i: Joomi am, sabu ko majjinir…óaa mi kon, ma mi labinan …ìe geddi …óin ka leydi, ma mi majjin …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe e laawol focciingol ngol."
  15,40,"Si wanaa …ìen …ìe su…ìi…óaa e jeyaa…ìe Maa fii ko rewa Maa."
  15,41,"Alla daali: Ngol ko laawol fotondirngol, hewtinayngol ka Am."
  15,42,"Pellet, jeyaa…ìe Am la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen, a alanaa…ìe …ìen kattal, a hippataa kadi bewnugol …ìe, si wanaa …ìen jokku…ìe ma e majju…ìe …ìen."
  15,43,"Pellet Jahannama wonii fodoore Ibuliisa e …ìen jokku…ìe mo e majju…ìe …ìen fow."
  15,44,"Jahannama no mari dame jee…ói…ói ka …ìe naatirta, damal kala e majje no heertinanaa jokku…ìe Ibuliisa …ìen ka naadiree."
  15,45,"Pellet, hulu…ìe Joomi mun …ìen, …ìe …óoftii yamirooje Makko …ìe wo…ó…óitii e ha…óaa…ói Makko, …ìen wonii e aljannaaji e …ìulli."
  15,46,"∆Åe wi'anoyte tuma …ìe naatata: Naatiree …ói hisugol e kala √±awu, da…óoo…ìe e kala kulol."
  15,47,"Men itti kala ko woni e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe immorde e konnaagu e ngayngu. ∆Åe wonti musi…ó…ìe yi…óindir…ìe, joo…óoday…ìe e nda…ó…óule hi…ìe ndaarindira."
  15,48,"Tampere he…ìataa …ìe ton, …ìe wonaa kadi yaltintee …ìe ton. Ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe nder ton."
  15,49,"An Nulaa…óo, anndin jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen, wonnde ko Min woni Haforanoowo tuubu…óo e ma…ì…ìe, Hinnotoo…óo …ìe."
  15,50,"Anndinaa …ìe wonnde lepte Am …óen, ko …óen woni lepte muusu…óe …óen. Yo …ìe tuubu …ìe ruttoo e Am fii no Mi haforana …ìe, …ìe da…óa lepte Am."
  15,51,"Humpitaa …ìe kadi fii Malaa'ikaa…ìe ho…ì…ìe Annabi Ibraahiima …ìen addannoo…ìe mo welo-welo …ìi…ó…óo gorko e halkeede yim…ìe Luuti …ìen."
  15,52,"Tuma nde …ìe naatunoo ka makko …ìe wi'i: ""Salaam (Kisiyee mon)"". O jaa…ìori …ìe ko …ìuri …óum mo∆¥∆¥ude, o …ìa…ónani …ìe ngaari ju…óaandi ngam …ìe √±aama, sikkugol ko …ìe …ìanndinke. Nde …ìe ronkunoo √±aa-mude, o wi'i: Menen ko men …óen∆¥ii …ìe on."
  15,53,"Malaa'ikaa…ìe imminaa…ìe …ìen wi'i: wata a …óen∆¥o, menen men humpitete ko welma: wonnde a he…ìay …ìi…ó…óo gorko ganndo."
  15,54,"Annabi Ibraahiima maakani …ìe - nde o ≈ãal…ói e ko …ìe wewliniri mo kon …ìi…ó…óo - : E on wewliniray lam …ìi…ó…óo e hoore ko mi nawyi kon mi ronkiti? E ko hon…óum wewlinirton mi?"
  15,55,"Malaa'ikaa…ìe imminaa…ìe …ìen wi'ani Ibraahiima: Men wewlinirii ma goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Wata a jeye e ta∆¥ii…ìe e ko men wewlinir maa kon."
  15,56,"Annabi Ibraahiima maaki: Hara no woodi Hara no woodi ta∆¥otoo…óo e yurmeende Joomi mun nden, si wanaa …ìen oo√±ii…ìe e laawol Alla focciingol ngol?"
  15,57,"Annabi Ibraahiima maakani …ìe: Ko woni fiiyaku addu…óo mon, onon …ìee imminaa…ìe Alla?"
  15,58,"Malaa'ikaa…ìe imminaa…ìe …ìen wi'i: Menen Alla nulu men halkugol tii…óu…ìe bonande, mawnu…ìe worodde …ìeen woni yim…ìe Luuti …ìen."
  15,59,"Si wanaa …ìeynguure Luuti nden e gom…óim…ìe jokku…ìe mo …ìen, Men da…ónday …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe e halkaare nden."
  15,60,"Si wanaa …ìeyngu makko, Men √±aawii on …óon ko heddotoo…óo e halkaare nden."
  15,61,"Nde Malaa'ikaa…ìe imminaa…ìe …ìen ardunoo ka …ìeynguure Luuti e mbaadi wor…ìe."
  15,62,"Annabi Luutu maakani …ìe: Ko on yim…ìe …ìe anddaaka."
  15,63,"Malaa'ikaa…ìe imminaa…ìe …ìen wi'ani Luutu: Wata a hulu. Ko woni, men addane an Luutu, …óen lepte …óe …ìe yim…ìe maa …ìe sikkitino e lepte halakooje …ìe."
  15,64,"Men addanii ma goonga ka jillaa gajaate. Pellet ko men goongu…ìe e ko men humpitu maa kon."
  15,65,"Yahdu e …ìeynguure maa nden ka tummbere jemme, iwtiraa …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe; hara gooto e mo'on ye∆¥∆¥itoraali …ìaawo ndaarugol ko tllii e mum en, rewon ka Alla yamiri on rewrugol …óon."
  15,66,"Men anndiniri Luutu ka wahayu, on fiyaaku mo Men √±aawi: wonnde …ìee yim…ìe …óoo, …ìe …óoofrete ka asli mum en ngam halkudebe si…ìe naati ka subaka."
  15,67,"Yim…ìe saare Saduum nden ari hi…ìe wewltora ho…ì…ìe Luutu …ìen, tam∆¥inagol yanirgol e ma…ì…ìe faahishaaku."
  15,68,"Annabi Luutu maakani …ìe: ∆Åee …óoo yim…ìe ko ho…ì…ìe am, wata on wirtiram ko faala…óon yanirde e ma…ì…ìe."
  15,69,"Huliree Alla accugol nguu faahishaaku. Wata on hoyniray …óee kuu…óe mon kaanu…óe."
  15,70,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo: E men ha…óaali ma weernugol gooto e yim…ìe …ìen?"
  15,71,"Annabi Luutu maakani …ìe himo ngantinanoo hoore-makko yesso ho…ì…ìe …ìen: ∆Åee …óoo ko jiw…ìe am jeyaa…ìe e resetee…ìe mon. Resee …ìe si wonii ko ittugol tuuyu faandi…óon."
  15,72,"Mi woondirii nguurndam maa an Nulaa…óo, pellet yim…ìe Luutu …ìen wonii e bewre tuuyu ma…ì…ìe, hi…ìe rutti-ruttinnoo(denngi-denngina)."
  15,73,"Sowto haacaango ngon halkiri …ìe ka pu…óal naange."
  15,74,"Men wayliti saare ma…ì…ìe nden, Men wa…ótiri dow on ley. Men saa∆¥ini e ma…ì…ìe kaa∆¥e iwru…óe e loope ju…óaa…óe."
  15,75,"Wonii e koo ko jantaa e ko yani e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen, immorde e halkaare, maandeeji wonnde …ìen taskotoo…ìe."
  15,76,"Pellet, ca'e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen no e laawol tabitngol fe∆¥∆¥oowo kala e setee…ìe …ìen no yi'a …óe."
  15,77,"Wonii e ngol pe∆¥∆¥ol, tinndinandewonande goom- …óim…ìe waajitoray…ìe …ìen."
  15,78,"Gom…óii yim…ìe Su'aybu …ìen yim…ìe fitaare fiiltiinde kadi ko too√±unirnoo…ìe yeddugol Alla fenna Nulaa…óo Makko on Su'aybu (yo o his)."
  15,79,"Men yottorii e ma…ì…ìe nanngirgol …ìe lepte. Pellet, ca'e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen e ko…óan…óe yim…ìe Su'aybu …ìen, wonii e laawol …ìanngangol wonande fe∆¥∆¥oowo."
  15,80,"Gom…óii Samuuda'en fennii, …ìen woni yim…ìe aynde Hijiri nden (Hakkunde Hijaz e Saami). ∆Åe fenniri Nulaa…ìe …ìen fow fennugol Annabiijo ma…ì…ìe on Saalih (yo o his)."
  15,81,"Men addani …ìe hujjaaji e maandeeji goongin…ói mo e ko o addi kon immorde ka Joomi makko, wano ngelooba mban, kono …ìe ronki waajitorde."
  15,82,"Hari hi…ìe ta∆¥iraynoo pelle …óen fii mahugol cuu…ói ka …ìe ho…óira da…óugol ko …ìe huli."
  15,83,"Haacaango lepte ngon nanngiri …ìe ka subaka."
  15,84,"Kon ko …ìe laatinoo hi…ìe faggitoo immorde e jawle e ko…óan…óe, fow nafaano …ìe e du√±ugol lepte Alla …óen."
  15,85,"Men tagiraali kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e ko woni hakkunde majji kon meere nde aldaa e √±ee√±al. Men tagiraali …óin fow si wanaa e goonga. Pellet, darngal ngal ko arayngal feere mun alaa. An Nulaa…óo, …óuurno fennoo…ìe ma …ìen, yaaforano-…óaa …ìe yaafagol labaangol."
  15,86,"Tabitii ko Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, woni Tagu…óo kala huunde, Anndu…óo …óum."
  15,87,"Gom…óii Men okkii ma Faatiha ngol Aayeeje jee…ói…ói, ko ngol woni fii Alqur'aana mawnde nden."
  15,88,"Wata a na…ìir gite maa …óen e nooneeji …ói Men dakmiri heefer…ìe …ìen sabu ko gasooji, wata a suno e ko …ìe fennata kon, yankinano gom…óim…ìe …ìen."
  15,89,"Maaku an Nulaa…óo: Min ko mi jertinoowo e lepte, …ìanngu…óo jertinaango."
  15,90,"Mi…óo jertinira on nde he…ìata on sugu ko Alla jippinnoo e …ìen senndir…ìe defete Alla …ìen pecce-pecce, …ìe gom…óina yoga …ìe yedda yoga."
  15,91,"∆Åen wa…óu…ìe Alqur'aanaare nden ge…ìe-ge…ìe, …ìe wi'i nde jilli mbilewu maa daari maa gim…ói."
  15,92,"Mi woondirii Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, Ma Men lanndoyo denndaangal …ìen wa…óu…ìe Alqur'aana ge…ìe-ge…ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  15,93,"Ma Men lanndoyo …ìe fii ko wonunoo e huuwude, immorde e keeferaaku e yaddugol ka aduna."
  15,94,"Fe√±√±in, an Nuaa…óo, ko Alla yamir-maa fe√±√±ingol ko noddugol e Makko, wata a ye∆¥∆¥ito e ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen wowlata huuwa."
  15,95,"Wata a …óen∆¥o …ìe. Menen Men heediii ma e pewje jalkitoo…ìe jeyaa…ìe e ardii…ìe heefer…ìe Qurayshi …ìen."
  15,96,"∆Åen wa…ótidoo…ìe e Alla rewetee…óo goo. Aray ka …ìe annda wattannde bone sirku ma…ì…ìe on."
  15,97,"Gom…óii Me…óen anndi, wonnde an Nulaa…óo, fonndo maa ngon hino …ìi…ótora ko …ìe fennata maa …ìe jalkite kon."
  15,98,"Fa…ìtor(moolo) ka Joomi maa la…ì…ìinirgol Mo ko O haandaani, mantiraa Mo sifaaji kamal, laato-daa e rewoo…ìe Mo …ìen juulannoo …ìe Mo. Ko e …óum lekki …ìi…ótagol fonndo maa woni."
  15,99,"Duumo-…óaa e rewugol Joomi maa fotde hi…óa wuuri haa maayde nden tawe e …óum."
